OL,3,CBudapest declared European tram driver
OL,4,Cchampion
OL,6,FBudapest has been declared the winner
OL,7,Fof the European Tramdriver
OL,8,FChampionship in the annual competition
OL,9,Fin Frankfurt.
OL,11,FEach public transport agency entered
OL,12,Fhas two drivers - one man and one
OL,13,Fwoman - who each get one chance to
OL,14,Fprove their skills through a series of
OL,15,Ftram tasks.
