OL,4,Cchampion
OL,6,FEach round consists of six disciplines
OL,7,Fof the following: stopping at a
OL,8,Ftarget, emergency braking, measuring
OL,9,Fside clearance during a curve, speed
OL,10,Festimation with a hidden speedometer,
OL,11,Fprecision driving past a gate,
OL,12,Fstopping at a tram stop, tram
OL,13,Fbilliards and tram bowling.
OL,15,FPoints are then awarded based on speed
OL,16,Fand skill. In many of the challenges
OL,17,Fthere is a water container at the
OL,18,Ffront of the tram - the more liquid
OL,19,Fspilled, the bumpier the journey,
OL,20,Fwhich leads the driver to lose points.
