OL,3,CBudapest declared European tram driver
OL,4,Cchampion
OL,6,FAfter a fierce contest, Budapest was
OL,7,Fdeclared the winner, with 3850 points,
OL,8,Fjust 50 points more than Brussels, who
OL,9,Ffinished 2nd.
OL,11,FThe first European Tramdriver
OL,12,FChampionship took place in Dresden in
OL,13,F2012 to celebrate the 140th
OL,14,Fanniversary of the city's tram network.
OL,16,FThe contest has happened every year
OL,17,Fsince, apart from in 2020 and 2021
OL,18,Fwhen it didn't go ahead because of the
OL,19,FCovid-19 pandemic. It draws a big
OL,20,Fcrowd of tram enthusiasts both in the
OL,21,Fhost city and online on the livestream.
